text:
Module mod-so included in 1.3.29 distribution does not recognize ClearModuleList 
directive, although it should know it. Can it affect funcionality of the server and 
system stability?
creator: starman@inmail.sk
slive@apache.org
text:
ClearModuleList is a function of the core server, not of a module.

Can you be more specific about what bug you are reporting.

No further response; assuming issue resolved. Feel free to reopen the report, if
you can supply the requested information.

Thanks for using Apache.
creator: nd@perlig.de
